item.title: Vampire Movie Draft
item.description:
Chad and Chris are back and we're doing something completely different, a movie draft! Not sure what that is? Don't worry, we explain it in the episode. And since it's October, Chad chose vampire movies as the subject of the draft. We choose 5 movies each and talk about even more than that towards the end.

Make sure to vote on twitter/X @ynfmoviepod for who you think had the best draft!
